## #interrupt-cells

Specifies the number of `<u32>` cells required to encode an interrupt specifier for the interrupt controller.

```dts
/* arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/sm8550.dtsi */
gic: interrupt-controller@17100000 {
    compatible = "arm,gic-v3";
    #interrupt-cells = <3>;
};
```
